{"tid":1126011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撤回修訂《引渡條例》遊行  日期：2019年4月28日 時間：下午3:00集合，4:00起步 集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T06:51:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1de246bd120797cad11045ede9d61ca7048336","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"撤回修訂《引渡條例》遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年4月28日<br />\n時間：下午3:00集合，4:00起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n<br />\n*天文台指當天會下雨，民陣請各位帶黃傘上街！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Withdraw Extradition Law Amendment&rdquo; March<br />\nDate: April 28<br />\nTime: assemble at 3:00 PM, march starts at 4:00 PM<br />\nVenue: East Point Road, Causeway Bay<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/58379598_2218835718163807_7896806670917959680_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=cc1330806b861c519db2741abb98b382&amp;oe=5D3A50D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F58379598_2218835718163807_7896806670917959680_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dcc1330806b861c519db2741abb98b382%26oe%3D5D3A50D2&h=3f1a6cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/rpp.511608535553209/2218835714830474/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Frpp.511608535553209%2F2218835714830474%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=2688c9f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/rpp.511608535553209/2218835714830474/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n大家盡可能黃衫黃傘"},{"pid":"01270929d914f763d5fbddea0a141b142a99005e","tid":1126011,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"又要俾仇狗笑跟泛民大隊舉港獨旗，屌你老母，你玩曬啦！"},{"pid":"5709a62bbe4a805e06d8ba55d42e715ce9a68d8d","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"後日"},{"pid":"4abca1aa907b0b2844e1741df074a334c369e35f","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"何以集會 ？ 何獎以遊行 ？ 何以示威？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20171228/20256907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F20256907&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=b0f7fb94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F20256907&h=d29fdc4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20171228/20256907</a><br />\n<br />\n何以示威？ - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n名采論壇 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十二月十四日，《蘋果日報》報道香港立法會在朝派之修改會議章條：「立法會外，反對修改的示威者無懼寒風，繼續留守。」十二月十日，《蘋果》也曾報道北京當局之驅逐無產工人：「北京多個地區爆發大規模遊行示威，示威者高喊：『暴力驅趕，侵犯人權！』」所謂「示威」和「示威者」，當然是英文demonstration、demonstrator的惡譯，而這惡譯應是清末民初人手筆，已是多年通用。<br />\n<br />\n英文demonstration、demonstrator等字，出自拉丁文的demonstratus，原意是「顯示」，根本沒有「威」的意思。而在新中國，「示威」者更完全無「威」可言：香港立法會外那三兩百人，北京若干地區街上那幾百遊行者，對當局來說，不值一哂。即使「示威」人數增加十倍百倍，當局何懼之有。謂予不信，請看二零一四年香港佔領運動，以及一九八九年北京天安門事件。<br />\n<br />\n「示威」必須有「威」可「示」。《左傳．文公七年》晉國郤缺指出，要做諸侯盟主，必須恩威並用：「叛而不討，何以示威？服而不柔（安撫），何以示懷（關懷）？非威非懷，何以示德？無德，何以主盟？」又《西漢演義》第八十八回漢高祖縛楚王韓信，數其罪狀，其一是出入都盛陳甲兵：「無事陳兵出入，以示威武，使四方見之者莫不寒心。」沒有實力聲討對方，使對方心寒，而曰「示威」，未免名不副實。所以，要說英文的demonstration和demonstrator，我一般會用「遊行抗議」、「集會支持」、「抗議者」、「支持者」等詞，不會動輒「示威」。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就是demonstration<br />\n<br />\n就是表態</span>"},{"pid":"54780396daae4b165e5df9b5bc8b0138753bc98f","tid":1126011,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"支持 會到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f233371718714b1d1313744c77398cfdc46e819","tid":1126011,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8d3b44951c498e6f2bfd2040699364b94347deb2","tid":1126011,"uid":41704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0b0bba2dd48b2b872b0ff94e8108bc6d70aecb8","tid":1126011,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"建議以暴力抗爭！！"},{"pid":"090ab3758cc20c8dac8f595bc50b3bf68abeb695","tid":1126011,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"港共一定立完法然後頭兩年唔引用<br />\n尤其唔會用黎引渡大劉<br />\n之後等冇晒聲先再用"},{"pid":"9592fc45f90dcb987337ade383ab4335d8e5e8e9","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"今日竟然比我買到把黃色縮骨遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b61ebd59ae391610f4ab3a1e4cee2ccf511186a","tid":1126011,"uid":3649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"冇黃傘不過聽日單拖一個人都會到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5697ed14753b1f5895ab63bb33622acd5dd37179","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b61ebd59ae391610f4ab3a1e4cee2ccf511186a","tid":1126011,"uid":3649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"冇黃傘不過聽日單拖一個人都會到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4740026e9a39b062ec96a5f1b99640dc5a7fd87e","tid":1126011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"